data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Located in a quiet, friendly neighborhood, this home offers a slice of Florida paradise. The NEW ROOF (DEC. 2022) provides peace of mind and enhances the home's aesthetic appeal. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills the spacious living area, thanks to large slider doors which offer picturesque views of the outdoors. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it the heart of the home. The primary suite is a tranquil retreat, featuring generous closet space and an en-suite bathroom for added convenience. This three bedroom home also offers one bonus room or what most would call a den, allowing for flexibility to suit your needs. Step outside where a screened lanai offers the perfect spot to enjoy morning coffee or alfresco dining. The backyard is an outdoor opportunity waiting to be explored, with plenty of space for gardening, playing, or just soaking up the Florida sunshine. North Port offers a unique blend of laid-back coastal living and vibrant community spirit. Enjoy the nearby beaches, parks, and nature preserves, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts. The city also boasts a range of shopping and dining options, along with a short 3 mile drive to the North Port Aquatic Center; it's an invitation to experience the Florida lifestyle at its finest. This North Port gem is ready to welcome you with open arms. Don't miss your chance to make this house your forever home – schedule a showing today and start living the Florida dream!
